Package models

Class Supervisor

java.lang.Object
models.User
models.Supervisor
public class Supervisor extends User
This class represents a Supervisor who can supervise projects in the system. It extends the User class and contains a list of supervised projects and methods to add and remove them. It also has methods to retrieve and update information about the supervisors from the database.
Author:
Timothy Lee, Justin Wong, Jun Hao, Lee Cheng Yao, Abhishekh
